      "content": "it's just so exhausting. the effort of trying to be seen, of pretending i'm actually part of the world... it feels pointless. sometimes it feels like the only way to actually get some peace is to just... go. like, if i just finished everything, would it even be a disruption? or would it just be quiet?",
